---
title: Reminder flow — server + local fallback + Mark Done
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant API as Fastify API
    participant Q as BullMQ (Redis)
    participant W as Reminder Worker
    participant FCM as FCM / APNs
    participant N as Notifee (local)

    User->>App: Toggle "Remind me" on task
    App->>API: PATCH /tasks/:id { remindEnabled: true }
    API->>Q: Enqueue next 14 occurrences<br/>(jobId = taskId + YYYYMMDDHHMM)
    API->>App: 200 OK
    App->>N: Schedule next 14 days locally<br/>(same notificationId)

    Note over Q,W: Wait until delay elapses

    Q->>W: Job fires
    W->>W: Check task exists, user active,<br/>not in quiet hours
    W->>FCM: Send push to user's device tokens<br/>(payload incl. Mark Done action)
    FCM->>App: Push delivered

    alt Foreground
        App->>App: Show Neumorphic in-app banner
    else Background + locked
        FCM->>User: System notification with action button
        N->>User: Local fallback (if no network)
        Note over FCM,N: OS dedupes via same notificationId
    end

    User->>FCM: Tap "Mark Done" on lock screen
    FCM->>API: POST /completions (via app background task)
    API->>API: Idempotent insert<br/>(UNIQUE taskId,userId,date)
    API->>API: Update Streak in same tx
    API-->>FCM: 201 { streak }

    W->>Q: Enqueue day-15 occurrence<br/>(rolling window)
